SUB_W14_EVAR_BOFO_CHAIR_100_CUT_000_030.text:
Oh, we've no interest in you whatsoever;
all we want to know is where to find more
triangles. Can you help with that?

SUB_W14_EVAR_BOFO_VISION_WITCH_000_CUT_0.text:
Ah, you there. What auspicious timing.
Go hunt that fiend over there for me;
I need its claws for various potions.

SUB_W14_EVAR_BOFO_001_CUT_000_000.text:
The triangle has transformed into
an evil spirit. You are strong;
you must do battle against it.
